class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T12:58:38.000Z","msg":"代表有55%機率適合你呢種人"},{"pid":"57894beaa9d188886461e6d35858351a242835b6","tid":2317110,"uid":258967,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:01:14.000Z","msg":"你地唔記得毒撚係零 0 x 0.55 = <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5511287d38f6c2b81c7c9cfacf8767887a22f80f","tid":2317110,"uid":365352,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"84fdc33c35b8b1c2830271f622b702d1e6d8c48a","tid":2317110,"uid":64953,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:54:47.000Z","msg":"命運計劃"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:03:44.000Z","msg":"我以為係卡通片姐點知係真嫁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d045b00c237156a782a601fe9951c9decb39b71d","tid":2317110,"uid":34241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:08:37.000Z","msg":"55%即係一係中一係唔中<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"582108d7159d6cb15bbc315849100b1979ae3f89","tid":2317110,"uid":199739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:14:47.000Z","msg":"點攞data train<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n姐係幫普通情侶做性格test+個人資料+訪問佢地而家對relationship滿唔滿意咁？<br />\n<br />\n我覺得result果part好難有準確data wo"},{"pid":"a04c98f73bba670b37c0d0a144eef523fcf8a33f","tid":2317110,"uid":20658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:27:46.000Z","msg":"毒撚對毒撚？"},{"pid":"9ff955e02198393bdbffed8719977bd9100ddc7b","tid":2317110,"uid":42870,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be0cfcabb1a29b2ddc723e213861e3cefe5d09ff","tid":2317110,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T10:25:47.000Z","msg":"不少人可能覺得難以覓得合適的伴侶。根據日本媒體報導，日本政府引入 AI 系統，推出婚介服務「AI愛」，不會為參加者提出的擇偶條件作出配對，而會根據雙方的潛在默契度進行推薦，而當中在日本埼玉縣，有 21 對情侶，於 2019 年透過 AI 推薦的婚介服務，成功配對。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，日本福井縣等 10 個縣，已經引入 AI 系統，推出婚介服務「AI愛」，為參與者覓得可能會對自己有好感的人，即使對方是不符合參與者的擇偶條件，亦都會推薦予參與者。<br />\n<br />\n據報導，目前日本有 25 個縣推出政府婚介服務，會根據參與者所提出的擇偶條件進行推薦，而在日本埼玉縣，於2019 年有 38 對情侶透過政府婚介服務而結婚，當中透過 AI 推薦，成功配對的情侶達 21 對，成功率達55%。而政府 AI 婚介服務費用約 1 萬至 2 萬日圓（約港幣 HK$ 745 至 HK$1490）。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府負責人表示，希望此服務能幫助更多人結婚。而日本政府計劃增加此服務的資源，計劃在 2021 年投入至少 20 億日元。根據日本厚生勞動省數據，日本當地結婚數目由 2000 年的 80 萬對，下跌至 2019 年的 60 萬對。<br />\n<br />\n資料來源： cnBeta<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://unwire.hk/2020/12/08/japan-ai-help-people-find-their-partners/fun-tech/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Funwire.hk%2F2020%2F12%2F08%2Fjapan-ai-help-people-find-their-partners%2Ffun-tech%2F&d=If5g8ybbdlMRYcYioqq3W%2FUbXA8pdDK36CymbYVYMuw%3D&h=cd92fba2\" target=\"_blank\">https://unwire.hk/2020/12/08/japan-ai-help-people-find-their-partners/fun-tech/</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-08T13:48:32.000Z","msg":"55%, 一係結，一係唔結"}]}